des: Nicolaas Pascal Migliore, was born on January 13,2000 and born in Chalmette Louisiana, He is an actor known for “Little Baby Eyes” (2009), and “Nicabob” (2017), he creates vlogs for his YouTube channel which is known as “Nicolaas Migliore Vlog” (2017-present), and Known for his new comedy series “Nicolaas Migliore Daily” (2019).
